item.title: Trustful Hands - The Dø
item.description:
Trustful Hands - The Dø

There's not enough hours in the day for all the European dance bands I fall in love with.  I am stressed with all the Dø's music videos I have to now watch and songs I have to memorize.

item.title: I think what I love about Neko Atsume is that when i check in on the yard all the cats are happy to see me, instead of ignoring me for no reason or angrily vomiting into my laundry hamper because of some twisted emotional negotiation I can't figure out.
